data.description: Assumable VA loan at 3.00%. Move in ready 3 bed, 2 bath home in the heart of Medford, close to shopping, schools, entertainment and services! The home has been nicely updated with custom cabinets, counters, appliances and lighting in the kitchen, custom tile shower in the primary bathroom, extensive hardwoods, vinyl windows throughout, updated recessed lighting, a certified fireplace insert and a metal roof. It's situated on a nearly 1/4 acre lot with a huge backyard, equally spacious covered patio, attached two car garage plus space for an RV. A great home, great location and an affordable price, don't wait to tour this one!
